SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO,ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO,ACCC_MUTTYPE, cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT) as decimal(18,2)) ,cast(sum(ACCC_MUTARETENTION) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTADISPUTES) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTASPECIAL) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTASTOCK) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN) as decimal(18,2)) ,cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTADEBTORS) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTARESERVE) as decimal(18,2)),cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT) as decimal(18,2)) FROM :3/accc,:3/tcod WHERE TCOD_ADMNO=ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO AND TCOD_CLNTNO=ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO AND TCOD_REPORTTYPE='MKO' and month(accc_acct_date) = :1 and year(accc_acct_date) = :2 and accc_muttype < 98 GROUP BY ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO,ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO,ACCC_MUTTYPE ORDER BY ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO,ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO, ACCC_MUTTYPE FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
